### VIP FLOW BOT - Arquivo de teste das rotas
### Use com a extensão "REST Client" do VS Code
### https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = seu_token_aqui

### ===== 1. HEALTH CHECK =====

GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### ===== 2. AUTENTICAÇÃO =====

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@vipflow.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### ⚠️ Copie o token da resposta acima e coloque em @token

### Pegar dados do usuário logado
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== 3. FOTOS =====

### Listar fotos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/photos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar foto (simula upload)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/photos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "uploads/foto_teste_1.jpg",
  "url": "http://localhost:3000/uploads/foto_teste_1.jpg"
}

### Criar segunda foto
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/photos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "uploads/foto_teste_2.jpg",
  "url": "http://localhost:3000/uploads/foto_teste_2.jpg"
}

### Pegar foto específica
### Mude o ID (1, 2, 3) se necessário
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/photos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Deletar foto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/photos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== 4. LEGENDAS =====

### Listar todas as legendas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/captions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar legendas por categoria
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/captions?category=soft
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar legenda (soft)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/captions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Você já conhece nosso conteúdo exclusivo?",
  "category": "soft"
}

### Criar legenda (curiosity)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/captions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Sabia que a maioria não sabe disso?",
  "category": "curiosity"
}

### Criar legenda (exclusivity)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/captions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Apenas para membros VIP...",
  "category": "exclusivity"
}

### Criar legenda (urgency)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/captions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Oferta válida apenas hoje!",
  "category": "urgency"
}

### Criar legenda (CTA - Call To Action)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/captions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Clique aqui e garanta seu acesso agora →",
  "category": "cta"
}

### Buscar legenda específica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/captions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar legenda
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/captions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Texto atualizado",
  "category": "soft"
}

### Deletar legenda
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/captions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== 5. CAMPANHAS =====

### Listar campanhas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar campanha
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Promoção Verão 2026",
  "startDate": "2026-05-21",
  "endDate": "2026-06-21"
}

### Criar segunda campanha
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Black Friday 2026",
  "startDate": "2026-11-01",
  "endDate": "2026-11-30"
}

### Buscar campanha específica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar campanha
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Promoção Verão - Atualizada",
  "startDate": "2026-05-21",
  "endDate": "2026-07-31"
}

### Mudar status da campanha (para paused)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "paused"
}

### Mudar status da campanha (de volta para active)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "active"
}

### Deletar campanha
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/campaigns/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== 6. AGENDAMENTOS =====

### Listar agendamentos de uma campanha
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules?campaignId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar agendamento
### ⚠️ Mude photoId (1, 2) e captionId (1, 2, 3, 4, 5) conforme seus dados
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campaignId": 1,
  "photoId": 1,
  "captionId": 1,
  "link": "https://seu-link.com/oferta",
  "scheduledAt": "2026-05-22T10:00:00"
}

### Criar segundo agendamento (amanhã às 14h)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campaignId": 1,
  "photoId": 2,
  "captionId": 2,
  "link": "https://seu-link.com/oferta",
  "scheduledAt": "2026-05-22T14:00:00"
}

### Buscar agendamento específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar agendamento (mudar horário)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduledAt": "2026-05-22T15:00:00",
  "link": "https://novo-link.com/oferta"
}

### Cancelar agendamento
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== 7. MÉTRICAS =====

### Ver histórico de publicações
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metrics/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ver histórico com limite (últimas 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metrics/history?limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ver estatísticas gerais
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metrics/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ver erros recentes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metrics/errors?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===== 8. TESTES DE ERRO =====

### Requisição sem token (erro 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/photos

### Token inválido (erro 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/photos
Authorization: Bearer token_invalido

### Email ou senha incorretos (erro 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@vipflow.com",
  "password": "senhaerrada"
}

### Rota não encontrada (erro 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rota_que_nao_existe

### Dados incompletos (erro 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/captions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Texto sem categoria"
}


### ===== 9. TELEGRAM =====

### Validar token (verificar se está correto no .env)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/telegram/validate

### Enviar mensagem de teste
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/telegram/test-message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chatId": "-123456789",
  "message": "✅ Teste de mensagem do VIP FLOW BOT!"
}

### Enviar foto de teste
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/telegram/test-photo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chatId": "-123456789",
  "photoUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/500x500",
  "caption": "📸 Prévia liberada!\n\nConteúdo completo no VIP",
  "link": "https://seu-link.com/oferta"
}

### Obter status do scheduler
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/telegram/scheduler/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Iniciar scheduler
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/telegram/scheduler/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Parar scheduler
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/telegram/scheduler/stop
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Executar agendamento manualmente (teste)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/telegram/schedule/execute
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduleId": 1
}


### ===== 10. MARKETING (SISTEMA PROFISSIONAL) =====

### Info do sistema de marketing
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/info
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar legendas por estratégia
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/captions?strategy=curiosidade&count=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar legendas: exclusividade
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/captions?strategy=exclusividade&count=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar legendas: urgência
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/captions?strategy=urgencia&count=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar legendas: oferta
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/captions?strategy=oferta&count=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar legendas: novidade
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/captions?strategy=novidade&count=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar legendas: chamada suave
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/captions?strategy=suave&count=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar legendas: CTA direto
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/captions?strategy=cta&count=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sugestões inteligentes - nível SUAVE
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/suggestions?callLevel=suave&count=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sugestões inteligentes - nível MÉDIO
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/suggestions?callLevel=medio&count=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sugestões inteligentes - nível DIRETO
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/suggestions?callLevel=direto&count=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Gerar combo automático (foto + legenda + estratégia)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/generate-combo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "photoId": 1,
  "campaignId": 1,
  "callLevel": "medio",
  "customLink": "https://seu-link.com/oferta"
}

### Gerar combo com estratégia específica
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/marketing/generate-combo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "photoId": 1,
  "campaignId": 1,
  "callLevel": "direto",
  "strategy": "urgencia"
}
